    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央のバンプロ入所から数ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few months after Rio joined Vanpro‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 3.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "――！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、今日はここまで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ that's all for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.633333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "やっと終わった～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally over",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "キッ、キツい～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-so tough",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう動けない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't move anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.133333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんな、来週までに私が注意した所を直してね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ make sure to fix the parts I pointed out by next week.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "あの、先生\n私にもアドバイスをお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ Sensei.\nCould you give me some advice too‚ please?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 26.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ああ、莉央は完璧だったから特に何も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rio‚ your performance was perfect‚ so there's nothing in particular…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいわ、貴方には新しいステップを教えてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I'll teach you a new step.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こっちに来なさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come over here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "はい\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ Sensei.\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 38.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんで莉央だけ特別扱いなのよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why is Rio the only one getting special treatment?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.3333333333385,
          "startTime": 41.46666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一番後輩なのに生意気よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's the most junior here‚ yet she's so cocky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生C",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……でも、あの子がへばってる私達と違うのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But we have to admit that she's different from us‚ who are all worn out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生C",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "認めるしかないよ……マジでデビュー近いかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She might seriously be close to debuting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん、あの子の練習量凄いよ。そこは素直に感心した",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ the amount she practices is insane. I have to admire her for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "例の話さ、きっと莉央が選ばれるんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know that rumor going around? I bet Rio is the one who'll be chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生C",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ probably.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "練習生C",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "悔しいけど莉央しかいないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's frustrating‚ but she's the only one who makes sense…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 66.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ…はぁ…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "（当然よ）\n（私はここの誰よりも歌もダンスも努力してきた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Of course.)\n(I've worked harder on my singing and dancing than anyone else here…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "（あの話、きっとモノにしてみせる……！）\n（いえ、もう私に決まってるわ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I'll definitely make that rumor a reality…!)\n(No‚ it's already decided! It's going to be me!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 82
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央はアイドル候補生達の中で異彩を放っており",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio stood out among the idol trainees‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "入所三ヶ月にして頭一つ抜けた存在になっていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and just three months after joining‚ she had become a cut above the rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ…はぁ…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――デビューまであと一歩",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Just one step away from debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "養成所の誰もがそう感じていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone in the training center felt it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 95.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "――！\nはぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――!\nPant Pant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央、お疲れ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "頑張っているな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're working hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 103.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_01_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん……\nいらしてたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san…\nYou were here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バンプロでも一、二を争う敏腕プロデューサー三枝信司",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Shinji Saegusa‚ one of the top producers at Vanpro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼に認められることが候補生全員の目標であった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be acknowledged by him was the goal of every trainee.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 114.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "レッスンの邪魔をしてはいけないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't want to interrupt your lesson‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "静かに見学させてもらっていたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I was quietly observing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあみんな、そのままでいいから聞いて欲しい",
      "translations": {
